window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>If only I'd never signed that contract. Or accepted the one I didn't.</p> <p>My husband doesn't trust me. Not that I can blame him.</p> <p>But he needs me, needs my image. I need his connections. And I have to find a way to convince him to set aside our differences.</p> <p>There's one way that always works.</p> <p>Even when we hate each other, our bodies betray us.</p> <p>The one place we've never disagreed is in bed.</p> <p>Except this is about more than just us.</p> <p>And even Luka Zoric's legendary control breaks sometimes.</p> <p>Book two of three.</p>"; 
